SELECT t0."UserId", t0."BioNote", t0."Price", t0."UnitOfPrice", t0."Id", t0."AccessFailedCount", t0."AvatarUrl", t0."ConcurrencyStamp", t0."Email", t0."EmailConfirmed", t0."FirstName", t0."IsActive", t0."LastName", t0."LockoutEnabled", t0."LockoutEnd", t0."NormalizedEmail", t0."NormalizedUserName", t0."PasswordHash", t0."PhoneNumber", t0."PhoneNumberConfirmed", t0."PublicUrl", t0."RefreshToken", t0."RefreshTokenExpiryTime", t0."SecurityStamp", t0."TwoFactorEnabled", t0."UserName", t1."ID", t1."CreatedOn", t1."IsDepricated", t1."LastModifiedOn", t1."SubjectID", t1."TutorID", t2."AvailabilityID", t2."TutorID"
FROM (
    SELECT t."UserId", t."BioNote", t."Price", t."UnitOfPrice", a."Id", a."AccessFailedCount", a."AvatarUrl", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."Email", a."EmailConfirmed", a."FirstName", a."IsActive", a."LastName", a."LockoutEnabled", a."LockoutEnd", a."NormalizedEmail", a."NormalizedUserName", a."PasswordHash", a."PhoneNumber", a."PhoneNumberConfirmed", a."PublicUrl", a."RefreshToken", a."RefreshTokenExpiryTime", a."SecurityStamp", a."TwoFactorEnabled", a."UserName"
    FROM "Tutors" AS t
    INNER JOIN "AspNetUsers" AS a ON t."UserId" = a."Id"
    WHERE t."UserId" = @__Id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t0
LEFT JOIN "TutorSubjects" AS t1 ON t0."UserId" = t1."TutorID"
LEFT JOIN "TutorAvaliabilities" AS t2 ON t0."UserId" = t2."TutorID"
ORDER BY t0."UserId", t0."Id", t1."ID", t2."AvailabilityID"
